Eng'eno o emodai


1  Etesheta eng'eno enkaji enye, eitasheyie ing'apeta enyena pokira naapishana. 
2  Neteyieng'a nkishu enyena, eitushula enaisho enye oo sabibu, neitobira sii emisa enye. 
3  Eirriwayie ninye nkaisiaayiak enyena meipotisho, toowuejitin neeika e nkanasa ejo, 
4  “Ore ilo pooki omoda, inchoo eibelekenyunye alotu ene.” Oilo le meeta ndamunot, ejo ninye, 
5  “Wou, inosa endaa ai, niok ina aisho oo sabibu naitushula. 
6  Tung'uai emodai pee inchu. Nilo te nkoitoi e ng'eno nagut.”


7  Ore ilo orerioo olasukenyani netum ninye emoroto, naa ore oloisikong oltung'ani torrono netum olbae. 
8  Minkok olasukenyani arashu kimbayu iyie; inkoo oltung'ani ng'en naa aikinyorru ninye iyie. 
9  Inchoo enkiteng'ena oltung'ani ng'en, naa keponaa eng'eno oleng, inteng'ena oltung'ani supat naa keponaa eng'eno enye.


10   Ore euriata o Laitoriani naa ninye enkiterunoto e ng'eno, naa ore eng'eno e ilo Sinyati naa eng'eno nagut. 
11  Amu te nanu eponari inkolong'i inono, aikiponikini iyie ilarin le nkishui. 
12  Tenaa ira iyie ng'en, naa aira ng'en te nkorrok ino; naa tinisukenyisho, naa iyie ake openy onap.


13  Ore enkitok namoda neilepilep; nemeutaroyu, nemeeta enkurruna nayiolo. 
14  Eton te nkutuk enkaji enye, neton too wuejitin neerupa enkanasa. 
15  Eipotu lelo oogiroo ine, lelo oopuo inkoitoi enye maate, 
16  ore pooki ng'ae omoda, inchoo eibelekenyunye alotu ene ore pooki ng'ae le meeta endamunoto ejoki, 
17  “Ore enkare napurruno naa kemelok, ore emukate nainosi too nkisudorot naa aisidai.” 
18  Kake meyiolo ninye ajo etii keeya ine, inchere ore lomon lenyena netii ineegut e nemeneng'a.

